=>direction:ltr etc , when u want to make arab website or text written
=>vertical align=> top,middel the text position will change 
=>text-decoration=>underline,overline,line-through,
=>text-transform=>uppercase,lowercase and capitalize
=>line-height=>30px, 0px ma overlap thia jase because they dont have height
=>text indent => first line of lorem will shift to 50px if we give in text indent
=>letter spacing => will give you space between each character
=>word spacing =>gap between words
=>white-space => pre,by default normal j hoy , nowrap
pre=>etle kevi rete bhi text rakhvo hoy evi rite rakhay
nowrap=>ekj line ma badha text nakhi devana
wordwrap=>breakword thi aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa half next line ma aay jase
